OL,3,CEverton lodge appeal against Premier
OL,4,CLeague after 10-point deduction
OL,6,FEverton confirmed they have lodged a
OL,7,Fformal appeal to the independent
OL,8,Fcommission which handed them a 10-
OL,9,Fpoint deduction by midday Friday.
OL,11,FThe club received the biggest
OL,12,Fsporting sanction in Premier League
OL,13,Fhistory after breaching financial
OL,14,Frules.
OL,16,FFollowing the deduction, CEO Colin
OL,17,FChong released a statement saying
OL,18,Fthey were "shocked and disappointed
OL,19,Fby the ruling" and believed "the
OL,20,Fsanction is disproportionate and
OL,21,Fwholly unjust".
